Class BTORepository

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.sc2002.ay2425.fcsdGroup2.repository.BTORepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
BTOStorageProvider
public class BTORepository extends Object implements BTOStorageProvider
Singleton Repository class for managing BTO projects, exercises, and applications. Handles loading from and saving to Excel files. Provides methods to add, retrieve, and persist data related to BTO operations.
